@startuml
actor Player
participant "Web UI" as Web
participant "API Backend" as API
participant "Auth Controller" as Auth
participant "DB" as DB

Player -> Web: Вводит логин/пароль
Web -> API: POST /auth/login
API -> Auth: validateCredentials()
Auth -> DB: SELECT user by email
DB --> Auth: user + password_hash
Auth -> Auth: verify password
Auth -> API: issue JWT + refresh
API -> Web: 200 OK + tokens
Web -> Player: Сохраняет сессию
@enduml
